<p id="subclass-overview-text" class="text-left mx-5 mb-5 p-2 rounded">
    <i>Your patron is a powerful entity with the power to easily bend the mind, bodies and soul of others to
        fulfill their ambitions, the Marionettist. Whether you enter this pact willingly or not, all that
        matters now is that you are no longer in control and when the strings are pulled, you better play your
        part.</i>
</p>

